### 6 Lindizgani Muchenjere   
 WATCH, YE SAINTS

 **1.**   
 Lindizganinge wakhristu,   
 Vyamchanya vyasunkhunyika;   
 Gozganinge nyali zinu,   
 Mukumane nayo Fumu.

 **Chorus:**   
 Wonani, Yesu wiza;   
 Wakwiza mu uchindami;   
 Wizamku wa Themba Lithu;   
 Wonani Yesu wiza.

 **2.**   
 Wonani phangano lake;   
 Wagowokera uheni;   
 Ndopa zasuka m'njilira;   
 Pharazga za kuwombokwa.

 **3.**   
 Mathemba ghakumbwambwantha;   
 Pulika lye wakwiza;   
 Phara za uchizi wake;   
 Apo mbata yikulira.

 **4.**   
 Mitundu yose yam'mara;   
 Khristu wakwiza luwiro;   
 Charu nacho chikumara;   
 Fumu yithu yikwizaso.

 **5.**   
 Yesu wakuchema mose;   
 Wakuweyerera imwe;   
 Endeska nyengo yamara,   
 Ungazakawa kuwalo.

### 28 Uwe Na Kanyengo   
 TAKE TIME TO BE HOLY

 **1.**   
 Uwe na kanyengo urombenge swi!   
 Uwazgenge mazgu mazuwa ghose;   
 Vwiranga wanyako awo mbatechi;   
 Vitumbiko vyake upenjepenje.

 **2.**   
 Uwe na kanyengo charu nchiheni;   
 Rombanga kwa Yesu na mtima wose;   
 Lawiska kwa Yesu na kumrondezga;   
 Kuti wanthu wanji wawone Yesu

 **3.**   
 Uwe na kanyengo wakurongozge;   
 Ungamrongozganga mu nthowa zak0;   
 M'vitima, m'kukondwa rondezga Fumu;   
 Gomezganga Yesu na mazgu ghake.

 **4.**   
 Uwe na kanyengo fwasa mu mzimu;   
 Wakurongozgenge mmaghanoghano;   
 Pakurongozgeka na mzimu wake;   
 Luwiro ufiske mlimo wa Fumu.

### 29 Mkharenge Nane     
 ABIDE WITH ME 29

 **1.**     
  M'kharenge nane, Fumu kwaıpa;   
Chisi nchikuru muenge nane;   
Para wovwiri wanji wazgewa   
Ndimwe mvwiri wane, muwe nane.   
Umoyo wa m'charu ntha ngwandanda

  **2.**     
  Viweme na vimwemwe vimare;   
Vikuzgoka na kuvunda vyose;   
Imwe ntha mkuzgoka, muwe nane.

 **3.**     
  Nkhumukhumbani mazuwa ghose;   
Wezi winu ukutonda mrwani Chirongozgi,     
 nchirikizgi ndimwe,   
Mu chisi na mhanya muwe nane.

  **4.**     
  Ntha nkhopaso para muli nane;   
Vyakuwinya ntha nkhuvipulika,   
Nyifwa na thegha ntha vikotyaso;   
Nkhuviruska uvwe muli nane.

  **5.**     
  Pakufwa murongore mphinjika;   
Muware m'chisi mundirongozge,   
Kuchanya kuche, pasi pafipe;   
Mu ghumi na m'nyifwa muwe nane.

### 31 Dazi La Mzimu   
 SUN OF MY SOUL

 **1.**   
 Dazi la mzimu mtaski 'mwe;   
 Mulipo, mdima palije   
 Bingu la pasi lireke,   
 Kumujandani kwa ine.

 **2.**   
 Na mise, apa nkhugona,   
 Ndipukwe nadi ku mtima;   
 Kugona tulo twa mzimu;   
 Pa chipakato cha Yesu.

 **3.**   
 Khalani nane na mhanya;   
 Kwambura imwe ndingafwa;   
 Khalani nane na mise;   
 Ndireke kuwa mu chisi.

 **4.**   
 Usange yumo wasovya;   
 Wapata lero wanangwa,   
 Mu m'wezge, wapera sono;   
 Wangagonanga m'kwananga.

 **5.**   
 Warwari mu walindenge;   
 Wakavu muwasambazge;   
 Tulo twa waranda tuwe;   
 Tuweme nga twa wa mjedu.

 **6.**   
 Mtitumbike pa kuwuka;   
 Mtisungilire pa kwenda,   
 Tisuke tibire tose,   
 M'chindimba cha wezi winu.

### 41 Chiuta Wa Msungilireni   
GOD BE WITH YOU

  **1.**   
  Chiuta wamsungilireni   
 mpaka tikakumaneso,   
 Warongozge wamsungeni;   
 Chiuta wamsungilireni.

  **Chorus:**   
 Mpaka tikurmane;   
 pamarundi gha Yesu;   
 Mpaka tikumane;   
 Chiuta wamsungiLireni.

  **2.**   
  Chiuta wamsungilireni,   
 ndiyo wamfukatireni;   
 Wampeniso na chakurya;   
 Chiuta wamsungilireni.

  **3.**   
  Chiuta wamsungilireni;   
 na para mukusuzgiKa,   
 yo ndi movwiri winu;   
 Chiuta wamsungilireni.

  **4.**   
  Chiuta wamsungilireni;   
 mwakutemwa kwake kose,   
 M urwani mose wasunge;   
 Chiuta wamsungilireni.
